data.description: INCENTIVES OFFERED WHEN USING SELLER PREFERRED LENDER. Welcome to Hidden Glen Community! Desirable neighborhood & well maintained home. Open floor plan with 9'ceilings, slab granite island & stainless steel appliances. Dine in kitchen with eat-up island & gas stove. Primary w/ensuite, vaulted ceilings & walk-in closet. Three additional bedrooms, loft area and laundry room complete the upper level. Triple pane windows, spray foam attic & interior sprinklers. Low maintenance yard, fenced, covered patio and gas hook up for grilling. Tankless hot water heater. HOA covers front yard care, wetland and park. Home has A/C and washer, dryer, garage overhead storage racks stay with the home.
